<h2 id="vlc-media-player">VLC media player</h2>
<hr />
<p>If youâ€™ve ever had a video file that you cannot play on your Mac then VLC is the tool you needed. This media player can play just about any video format. It can also convert any video it can play. VLC does also have some other features such as a stripped down media organizer which can come in handy.</p>

<p>VLC player will usually trigger this dialog telling you it is downloaded from the internet, or if it wonâ€™t open right click on the app and choose open.</p>

